**Stack:** {{e.g. .NET 8 / Angular / SQL Server / Azure / GitHub Actions}}
**Build / test / verify:** `{{BUILD_CMD}}` · `{{TEST_CMD}}` · `{{LINT_CMD}}`
**Done means the hook lets you stop.** A change is finished when it is proven against its
